for filing with the Director under the CBCA, the articles of arrangement and such other documents and instruments as are necessary or
desirable to give effect to the Arrangement in accordance with the Arrangement Agreement, such determination to be conclusively evidenced
by the execution and delivery of such articles of arrangement and any such other documents or instruments.</TD></TR></TABLE>

