course expenses). Other than in the ordinary course or as set forth in Section&nbsp;11 of the Company Disclosure Schedule, there are
no Contracts with, or advances, loans, guarantees, liabilities or other obligations to, on behalf or for the benefit of, any shareholder,
director, officer or employee of the Company or any of the Company Subsidiaries, or any of their respective Affiliates or associates.</FONT></P>

