has obtained (or caused to be obtained) informed consent by or on behalf of each human subject who participated in the Company&rsquo;s
ongoing clinical studies; (ii)&nbsp;in using or disclosing patient information received by the Company in connection with the Company&rsquo;s
ongoing clinical studies, the Company, each Company Subsidiary and any contractor or other Person acting on their behalf have complied
